{"tid":1279868,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求文宣幫手，逃犯條例係搶錢條例，外資一定走（有詳解）","createTime":"2019-07-02T19:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:36:48.000Z","uid":263525,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"310f77795c05b51ef3f11ddc52dc9108eefa0a3d","tid":1279868,"uid":263525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:16:40.000Z","msg":"大家作為香港人，條例衰乜大家都知，但睇完懶人包，發覺有個point無人提過。如果有，我柒，任屌唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n其實，<span style=\"color: red;\">「外地沒收令」,才是逃犯條例的主角，因為可以在貿易戰時，只要大陸想，就可以輕輕鬆鬆凍結幾千百億的資金。因為佢地可以隨便生安白造某公司資金係涉及犯罪，甚至揾個阿巫去民事訴訟都一樣得。香港做生意的穩健基礎會一下子消失，所有外資係會走晒，亦永遠唔會有人信香港<br />\n<br />\n所以送中條例一定要徹！</span><br />\n<br />\nCAP525,S2（節錄）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/525/s2.html#external_confiscation_order\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F525%2Fs2.html%23external_confiscation_order&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc8mKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=d7202378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/525/s2.html#external_confiscation_order</a><br />\n<br />\n外地沒收令 ( external confiscation order )指根據香港以外某地方的法律，為下述目的而作出的命令 &mdash;&mdash;追討在與外地嚴重罪行有關連的。。。。。（下删）<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">不論引致作出該命令的法律程序屬刑事抑或民事性質</span>，亦不論該等法律程序是以針對人抑或針對財產的形式進行的；<br />\n<br />\n外地嚴重罪行 ( external serious offence )指最高刑罰為死刑或不少於<span style=\"color: red;\">24個月監禁</span>的外地罪行；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCAP525,27（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n(1)凡香港以外某地方向律政司司長提出請求為以下事宜作出安排 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)強制執行外地沒收令<br />\n<br />\nCAP525,附件2（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n6.限制令及押記令可於甚麼情況下作出<br />\n(1)第7(1)及8(1)條賦予原訟法庭的權力，可於以下情況下行使 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)法律程序已在香港以外某地方提起；<br />\n(b)該等法律程序尚未結束；及<br />\n(c)外地沒收令已在該等法律程序中作出，或原訟法庭覺得有合理理由相信外地沒收令可能會在該等法律程序中作出。<br />\n(2)凡原訟法庭信納法律程序將會在香港以外某地方提起而法院覺得外地沒收令可能會在該等法律程序中作出，則上述權力亦可在此情況下行使。"},{"pid":"1f9223bc1a025b4ffd5675a26419ef65afbaa2d3","tid":1279868,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd65abd2925307ceecd1f2f4d3e5828f3d0068c7","tid":1279868,"uid":263525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:32:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"039c6f3f34b4979ecab4c3057a59e3983c0283d2","tid":1279868,"uid":263525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:38:14.000Z","msg":"再自推，熱門有人話已經唔需要講逃犯條例。真係大錯誤，電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a41ac47152c8b85f08c3e5fb434ad67cb6e6ad","tid":1279868,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"945dcad2b79ff66b944facbdcf25ea21adc3d0a8","tid":1279868,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:40:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20c8c554f279965a87f385f0f021a5f6023e01cf","tid":1279868,"uid":272822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:43:36.000Z","msg":"推!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6031c05ecd1808b6fd19830c2667fdf33da44499","tid":1279868,"uid":263525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:47:52.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a148e984c648a7ae3af12d854fde6ca7a6b0906","tid":1279868,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"我之前FF過，佢地想搞外